# Source: https://curl.se/windows/dl-8.5.0_1/curl-8.5.0_1-win64-mingw.zip
# (Shipped sum is for the extracted curl.exe, NOT the zip.)
2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2e  curl.exe

